{
  "application": "Docker",
  "details": {
    "resource_requirements": {
      "nodes": 1,
      "cpus": 40,

      "walltime": "0:05:00",
      "queue": "dgx",
      "project_code": "99999999"
    },
    "docker_image": "nvcr.io/nvidia/cuda:latest",
    "commands": [
      "pwd",
      "cd \"$PBS_O_WORKDIR\"",
      "pwd",
      "hostname",
      "nvidia-smi",
      "echo \"Container starts in the directory:\"",
      "pwd",
      "echo \"Change directory to where job was submitted:\"",
      "cd $PBS_O_WORKDIR",
      "pwd",
      "echo \"PBS_O_WORKDIR is set in shell:\"",
      "echo \"PBS_O_WORKDIR=$PBS_O_WORKDIR\"",
      "echo \"PBS_O_WORKDIR is not set in the container:\"",
      "echo \"PBS_O_WORKDIR=\$PBS_O_WORKDIR\"",
      "echo",
      "echo \"By default Docker starts in a private network with hostname different to that of host operating system:\"",
      "hostname",
      "echo",
      "nvidia-smi"
    ],
    "docker_run_options": [
      "-u UID:GID",
      "--group-add PROJECT",
      "-v /home:/home",
      "-v /scratch:/scratch",
      "-v /raid:/raid",
      "--rm",
      "-i",
      "--shm-size=1g",
      "--ulimit memlock=-1",
      "--ulimit stack=67108864"
    ]
  }
}
